---
title: Peach and Prosciutto Flatbread with Fresh Mozzarella and Balsamic-Arugula Salad
description: On this flatbread, salty prosciutto pairs perfectly with juicy peaches, while gooey melted cheese is o set by a tangy, peppery arugula salad. A final sprinkle of torn basil leaves is the pièce de résistance.
